  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed dormer extension would be an incongruous and alien feature that fails to respect the unity and rhythm of the conformed roofline along the terrace. The dormer would significantly alter the form of the roof, and will be detrimental to the character and appearance of the existing building and the street scene. The development is contrary to policies D4 (Designing in Context) and D11 (Alterations and Extensions) of Islington Council's Unitary Development Plan (2002), and Islington's Urban Design Guide (2006)."
